query:
SELECT d.code, d.name, COUNT(q.id) as question_count 
FROM pirIntegrityDimensions d 
LEFT JOIN pirIntegrityQuestions q ON d.id = q.dimensionId 
GROUP BY d.id, d.code, d.name 
ORDER BY d.displayOrder;
